"><TITLE>Experiment Cont... - www.ezboard.com</TITLE></HEAD><BODY TEXT=#CCCCCC BGCOLOR=#000000 LINK=#ffffff VLINK=#CCCCCC ALINK=#ffffff ><CENTER><CENTER><A HREF=#><IMG SRC=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/header_small.gif BORDER=0></A><P></CENTER><CENTER><a href="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/cscintro.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/banners/cscuserbanner.gif"></a></CENTER><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95%><TR><TD><B><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Graffë's Wizard Discussion</FONT></A></B><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Class Balance & Class Bugs</FONT></A></B><BR><B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Experiment Cont...</FONT></B></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddTopicScreenFromWeb><IMG SRC=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/new_topic.gif border=0></A>&nbsp; &nbsp; <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=276.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0></A></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=239.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=278.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><table border=0 width=95% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><TR><TD valign=top BACKGROUND= http://www.graffe.com/home/bar_back.gif><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>Author</FONT><B></TD><TD valign=top BACKGROUND= http://www.graffe.com/home/bar_back.gif><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>Comment</FONT><B></FONT></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=beljoda>BelJoda</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>6:47:54 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Experiment Cont...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">As some of you may or may not know, I started a Rogue about 4 weeks back, using my Wiz to Get him Items and such like...<br>
<br>
Hes in the 50's now and starting to group with ppl like my Wiz.... Here is what I have learned painfully about Wizards with my Rogue:<br>
<br>
Lesson 1 - Annoyance:  I was in Karnors, either in the Hand room or Skelly Tower, I cant remember exactly... the tanks were on the mob doing some major whuppage but then the Wiz decided to cast... He did a fair bit of Damage I suppose, he said he had a full hit, but the mob Agroed immediately on the Wiz meaning that the tanks were left on Auto attack getting Spammed by &quot;Your target is not in range&quot; or &quot;You cannot see your Target&quot;, while the Mob was busy beating down the Wiz... By the Time the Tanks were back on it, I had missed the Chance to Backstab (max 250 atm) once as well as do some 50+ damage about 12 times over, thats 850 damage from me alone and the other 2 tanks will have not been hitting in this time also... Meanwhile the Wizard was getting Badly hurt and Had to be CHealed for him to live... so the end result of 1 Wizard in group Nuking was a net LOSS in damage done to the Mob and the Waste of a CHeal to keep the Wizard alive..... Now how the HELL can a Wizard be considered remotely Group friendly.... By Casting once when the Mob was 70% health he actually LESSENED the effectiveness of the group... When you think about it like that, we would have been better of keeping the group at only 5 members and not bothering with a 6th (the Wizard), who just stole our exp and rolled on the loot we earned...<br>
<br>
lesson 2: - Raiding: Where to begin... thankfully most of the mobs summon here so overnuking just kills the Wizard rather than wasting good melee damage as the mob runs off... BUT there is still room for the Wizard to be useless, as you probably guessed already.... ok, raid begins, Wiz is useful for a few seconds as we are ported up... we settle in camp positions and begin pulling, Wizards nukes, most of the time at least one of them are over agroed and get summoned, Cleric wastes his CH's and Celestial Heals... Melees continue to whup the mob... The over agroing Casters (not always Wizards, but usually Wizards) are Rezzed if a CH is too slow... So how are they useless here? They seem to do NO damage (as far as I can tell) to the mob, the speed of mob hp bar reduction isnt even altered by a Wizard cast, generally the Wizards are seen to be sat down to, they soak up Cleric mana and when they get rezzed the Just sit for about 5mins doing nothing at all.... What is the Point? they dont even seem to effect the mob's health.... Wizards NEED to be Improved and until I see the an improvement in the Wizards I group with, the Rogue (who is a lower level) will be my Main character...<br>
<br>
I'm not trying to say the Wizard is without hope, I love playing my Wizard, its fun to see all that damage mounting up so quickly from just 1 character and Melees need them BADLY for Ports and such like, a Druid just couldnt stand the stress placed to port so many people around, but they are Flawed where grouping is concerned IMHO. They need improvement and they need it fast or more like me will use Wizards for Ports only... Verant hasnt taken into account the fact the a Wizard's spell casting, more often than not takes away from the other classes damage and therefor lessens rather than improves a group or a Raid...</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=beljoda>BelJoda</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>6:50:38 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Experiment Cont...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">P.S. please dont hate me for saying these things, I really think they need to be said for them to come out into the light and for them to begin to be Addressed and then Fixed... Without this kind of information nothing will ever get done as VI thinks the class is Fine as it is.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unicolheartsbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicol Heartsbane</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>8:12:37 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Experiment Cont...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Wizards do too much damage, and suck complete heals!  Heh.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucellessedai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Celles Sedai</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>9:22:19 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Experiment Cont...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I will tell you, I have a 51 rank wizzy and i am happy with her. However I spend most of my time soloing unless my guild is around in which they ask me to join them. That was about a month ago. I am still in the guild but I decided to start a cleric. I put up a LFG and within 10 sec I have a million replies flying at me and i get my choice of a pick. The sad thing is, I am starting to enjoy my cleric because I can group with people. I wish it wasnt so. I will say this again just give verants baby class the capabilities of the wizzy and let us choose what class we want to be that lvl. I wish verant wasnt so lazy and just would address the classes the really need it. Instead they put a sub game out,my guess is for the wizzy downtime when soloing, and now even though its a dumb game play it. The sad thing is I just got to wave 10 last night.Well we all have given many suggestions but verant cant get the wax out of thier ears to listen to us. Sooner or later there will be another game such as this to come out and verant may lose a lot of clientel. I am already geared for another rpg that is supposed to be out soon that actually has roleplaying in it.<br>
You can actually work with the npc's and get into political places in game. Plus when u die you have to go through the spirit world to get back to your body not lose major exp and appear naked. Until next time.<br>
