</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umajyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Majyn</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>9:58:43 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Hrm...</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I have my warrior now to 54. My wizard is/was 55. (Mostly retired.)<br>
