-Luclin Server</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarantir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arantir</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/15/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3:11:07 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">what?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">To the above poster, what?!  You want us to go into groups, say &quot;blah blah I suck you should never have taken me?!?&quot; that's just genius.  Why would we want to enlighten OTHER CLASSES as to how much we suck, we need to let VERANT know so he can fix us so the other classes won't ever know how much the wizard class is sucking.  High resists, not enough mana, too much aggro, not enough hp = A wizard.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=239.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=278.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=276.topic&index=5><IMG SRC=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=276.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub23.